                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930529-10-off47 t17930529-10-cd48"></join>, three muslin neckcloths, value 3 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17930529-10-victim181" type="victimName">
